description: If you're looking for the finest way to satisfy your hunger on the streets of Orlando, then there's nothing like a Bad As's Sandwich! There's no secret to this amazing menu, just house-cured meats, locally sourced produce, and fresh baked bread every day. A sandwich made fresh from only the best ingredients is always a great meal! Don't miss out on Orlando's most amazing sandwich shop on the move, grab yourself a Bad As's Sandwich today!
name: BAD AS'S SANDWICH
